{
  "total_duration": 430.601,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 24.04,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "周日的伦敦、下雨、你睡到自然醒、慢悠悠在吃早饭。突然亲戚电话打来：「我刚到火车站、这就来你家。」你接起电话——嘴里还嚼着面包。她问：「你在干啥？」你怎么回？主角的答案、让姑妈震惊到连说：「天——啊。」——今天咱们看这场英国老派守时观对上当代躺平派的喜剧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 24.39,
      "end": 39.262,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那是个星期天、主角说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I never get up early on Sundays."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——周日我从不早起、有时直接"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "stay in bed until lunchtime"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、躺到午饭点。这一天他也是、起得特别晚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 39.611,
      "end": 53.091,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他爬起来"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "looked out of the window"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、外面又黑又下雨——"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's raining again."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他心想：「鬼天气、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "What a day!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "」就在这时候、电话铃响了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 53.441,
      "end": 67.325,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是他姑母 Lucy 打来的、她说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I've just arrived by train. I'm coming to see you."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——刚下火车、这就来看你。主角一边吃东西一边接电话、来不及反应。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 67.674,
      "end": 87.49,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "姑妈听见他在嚼东西、问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "What are you doing?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主角老老实实回："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm having breakfast."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "姑妈震惊："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dear me, do you always get up so late? It's one o'clock!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——天啊、你总这么晚起吗？现在都一点了！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 87.84,
      "end": 92.76,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听完这个 Sunday morning 的小段子、你最想笑的地方在哪儿？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 93.11,
      "end": 95.743,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主角下午一点还在吃早饭？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 96.093,
      "end": 104.557,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对、但要理解为什么这事在英国特别滑稽、得先聊聊"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sunday roast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个传统。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 104.907,
      "end": 106.803,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Sunday roast 是啥？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 107.153,
      "end": 127.352,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "英式周日午餐——一家人在中午十二点到下午两点、围着烤牛肉 + Yorkshire pudding + 烤土豆吃饭、几百年传统。所以姑妈一句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's one o'clock!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的潜台词不是「现在晚了」、是「正经人这会儿在吃 Sunday roast、你居然刚起」。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 127.702,
      "end": 132.233,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "喔——震惊的不是他晚起、是他不在该有的节奏里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 132.583,
      "end": 147.735,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。英国人对「按部就班」有种执念、叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "punctuality"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、守时。下午一点还在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "having breakfast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、对老一辈英国人来说、几乎是离经叛道。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 148.084,
      "end": 154.001,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以姑妈那句"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dear me"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、不只是「天啊」、是「不是吧你」。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 154.351,
      "end": 166.855,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "没错。最妙的是最后——主角重复说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm having breakfast, I repeated."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "听起来一点没意识到问题、就是「我吃我的、关你啥事」。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 167.204,
      "end": 170.558,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就有点像现在的「躺平」吧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 170.908,
      "end": 181.772,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "哈、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Lesson 2"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的笑点核心、就是「英国老派守时观」对上「年轻人爱躺平」。咱听一遍英文原文。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 182.122,
      "end": 184.018,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was Sunday."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 184.368,
      "end": 187.224,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I never get up early on Sundays."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 187.574,
      "end": 190.766,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I sometimes stay in bed until lunchtime."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 191.115,
      "end": 193.923,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last Sunday I got up very late."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 194.273,
      "end": 196.553,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I looked out of the window."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 196.903,
      "end": 199.183,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was dark outside."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 199.533,
      "end": 202.749,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'What a day!' I thought."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 203.099,
      "end": 205.139,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'It's raining again.'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 205.489,
      "end": 208.297,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Just then, the telephone rang."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 208.647,
      "end": 211.023,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was my aunt Lucy."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 211.373,
      "end": 214.421,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'I've just arrived by train,' she said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 214.77,
      "end": 216.906,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'I'm coming to see you.'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 217.256,
      "end": 220.304,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'But I'm still having breakfast,' I said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 220.654,
      "end": 223.342,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'What are you doing?' she asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 223.692,
      "end": 226.644,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'I'm having breakfast,' I repeated."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 226.994,
      "end": 229.226,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'Dear me,' she said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 229.576,
      "end": 234.28,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'Do you always get up so late? It's one o'clock!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 234.63,
      "end": 237.27,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "until"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "until"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 237.62,
      "end": 239.348,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "until"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "until"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 239.697,
      "end": 265.777,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "until"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是「一直到……为止」、表示时间持续。课文里说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "stay in bed until lunchtime"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——躺到午饭那会儿。日常你会用到："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I will play until dinner."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——我一直玩到吃晚饭。注意它后面跟的是「时间点」、不是「时间段」。别说 until 3 hours、要说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "for 3 hours"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "或"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "until 3 o'clock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 266.127,
      "end": 268.951,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "outside"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "outside"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 269.3,
      "end": 270.956,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "outside"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "outside"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 271.306,
      "end": 298.17,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "outside"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是「在外面、外面」。可以作副词、也可以作介词。课文"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was dark outside"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——外面一片昏暗。和它对应的反义词是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "inside"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。日常说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Let's play outside."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——咱们出去玩。注意 outside 重音在第二个音节、读"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "out-SIDE"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、不是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "OUT-side"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 298.519,
      "end": 303.351,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "repeat"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词、其实是它的过去式形式："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repeated"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 303.701,
      "end": 305.477,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "repeat"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repeated"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 305.827,
      "end": 332.115,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "repeat"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "原形是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "repeat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、意思是「重复、再说一遍」。课文里他第二次说「我在吃早饭」、用的就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I repeated"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——「我又说了一遍」。这个词在英语里超级常用、老师上课经常说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Please repeat after me."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "——跟我念一遍。注意拼写、是 re-peat、不是 re-peet。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 332.464,
      "end": 365.972,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课的语法点：现在进行时——"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm having breakfast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It's raining"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm coming"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。规则就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "am/is/are + doing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、表示「现在正在进行的动作」。和上一课的过去进行时一对比就清楚了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I was having breakfast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是「我那时候正在吃」、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am having breakfast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是「我现在正在吃」。一个是过去的一个时刻、一个是说话的此时此刻、就差一个 be 动词的时态。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 366.322,
      "end": 388.621,
      "speaker": "A",
